@The International Centre

Calling all outdoor adventure enthusiasts! Score amazing pre-season deals on the latest outdoor gear and incredible travel destinations. Watch dynamic kayaking demonstrations at our White-Water Demo Pool and perfect your roll, conquer the Rock Wall, and fuel your love for biking, hiking, and climbing. Connect with seasoned guides who will help you find the ultimate trail and portage. Uncover exotic hot spots, safaris, eco-holidays, or weekend getaways. Be inspired by outdoor experts and popular online personalities who will be sharing their personal stories as well as advice. This is Canada’s largest collection of exhibitors offering the latest camping gear, paddle sports, outdoor clothing, scuba diving & ultimate adventure travel destinations!

Source: Toronto Events (Tockify)
